description: I normally wouldn't approach a guy like William. He's quite intimidating with his death tattoos and his tough look. The only reason it did happen is because he smiled at me. That kinda said: 'It's ok, I won't kill you !'. Looks can be deceiving, and it turned out that William is the sweetest guy, very open-minded and quite an exhibitionist to say the least !
title: William, Scene #01
